Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.32,0:00:13.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.08,0:00:19.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發旋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.37,0:00:22.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.71,0:00:31.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡是？朝倉？大家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.93,0:00:37.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.14,0:00:42.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不久他就會來迎接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.15,0:00:46.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.15,0:00:49.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.19,0:00:52.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.53,0:02:27.83,Title - blur,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1215,880)\bord0\blur10\fad(695,695)}她的困惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.53,0:02:27.83,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1215,880)\fad(695,695)}她的困惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.23,0:02:52.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.11,0:03:03.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉 在電話裡已經說過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 醒來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.79,0:03:11.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 在公園的椅子上睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎回來 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.40,0:03:40.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在回家的路上遇上事故了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.41,0:03:43.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事故？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 因為那場事故的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.79,0:03:49.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你睡上了一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我代替你作為長門有希而生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像超自然現象一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.13,0:04:00.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是那麼誇張的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在也只不過是一場夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.39,0:04:07.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大腦也只是在整理記憶中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.76,0:04:09.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要你醒過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.18,0:04:11.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像這種對話馬上就會忘記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.73,0:04:19.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你能告訴我睡著的時候發生的事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.40,0:04:22.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.95,0:04:28.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼啊 你剛才不是說在整理記憶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.45,0:04:32.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是大腦自發的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我自己並不希望發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我傳達了一樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.76,0:04:49.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,向他 把我的感情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.10,0:04:58.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個我做了件不得了的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.53,0:05:04.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,意思是說我傳達了我自己的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我當然明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.16,0:05:16.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來該你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.13,0:05:21.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.22,0:05:25.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.30,0:05:29.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喜歡同一個人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.26,0:05:31.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對方是他的話我也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 真沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.12,0:05:53.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然梅雨季節過後 衣服幹的就是快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.94,0:05:58.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要收衣服了 幫忙把籃子拿來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還真又回到遊戲上面去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.27,0:06:17.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喜歡看書喔 不過更喜歡遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你指的是漫畫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.69,0:06:22.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是喜歡看書的我比較好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.08,0:06:45.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是呢 說實話朝倉我並不喜歡遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是看書的你比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.18,0:06:51.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騙你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都怪你問那種刁鑽的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是回敬你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.06,0:06:58.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還在意著什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.86,0:07:08.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那天 我回來的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉因我感到高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是又感覺到哪裡有些寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那當然是了 事發突然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的陷入混亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.54,0:07:27.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我內心早就得出了結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對於我來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.18,0:07:38.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論哪個長門都無優劣之分 都是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.27,0:07:43.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以長門你不要想太多 做自己就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像平常一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.52,0:07:48.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我說說你就好了 是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.07,0:07:50.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.66,0:07:53.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,順便說一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.70,0:07:55.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說你事事要勞煩我你應該生氣才對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.91,0:07:56.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.12,0:08:00.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種反應 真的是長門回來了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還真是熱呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經是夏天了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.88,0:08:10.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要趕快去選泳裝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.42,0:08:11.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,泳裝？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.51,0:08:14.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假有很多活動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.43,0:08:15.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邀請阿虛一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼樣的才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要找到適合長門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早啊 阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.53,0:08:36.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,數學作業好好做了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.03,0:08:39.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可不要待會又慌慌忙忙抄我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.37,0:08:41.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是當然了 朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點借我抄吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉 這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.00,0:08:50.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我們對一下答案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.38,0:08:52.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我馬上就找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.59,0:08:54.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.76,0:08:55.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔 早…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.06,0:09:06.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天真熱呢 長門 太熱啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.69,0:09:09.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你到底抄不抄啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我到底在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.42,0:09:32.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.47,0:09:41.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.93,0:09:43.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,借你玩？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.14,0:09:46.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不不 你繼續吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.44,0:09:57.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.95,0:09:58.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都考得不錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}最吵的又回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.87,0:10:04.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假要用力地玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然很突然 阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.79,0:10:07.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道今天是什麼日子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的生日嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.21,0:10:15.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,順便一提我的生日是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.13,0:10:16.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那種事無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是拿你沒辦法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說說今天是幾月幾號？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七月七日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.60,0:10:28.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不會是在說七夕的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然是那件事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.52,0:10:35.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為今年的七夕我們所有社員要搞些隆重盛大的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要擅自決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說長門 聽說這個事了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有希 我不是在電話裡跟你說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欸 啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽說過了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.96,0:10:56.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話 阿虛和古泉 跟我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.55,0:10:59.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底要帶我們去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.18,0:11:01.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 快點啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.39,0:11:07.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔 那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.49,0:11:30.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你要我幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.54,0:11:31.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是廢話嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.29,0:11:35.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,選一些適合七夕的竹子砍下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 我記得這裡是私人用地啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想讓我們當竹子小偷嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.01,0:11:42.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:43.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已經提前呼嚨過所有者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,獲得了許可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種事情倒是幹得俐落呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.97,0:11:48.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,保險嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.35,0:11:51.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘛 就是這樣了 拜託了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.40,0:12:00.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說在前面 如果選的不好 就要重新砍喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.99,0:12:01.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.53,0:12:07.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 馬上就變回那種喧嘩的日子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼宮也是度過了枯燥的考試期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.37,0:12:13.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在心情正好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.29,0:12:17.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說你在這期間都在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔 我啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.47,0:12:21.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘛 發生了很多事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.30,0:12:27.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這麼說更讓人在意了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.64,0:12:28.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.89,0:12:31.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被吸血了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這…這什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 全都是斑蚊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這可真是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.99,0:12:45.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點砍完趕快出去 古泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.82,0:12:51.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 都已經是高中生了竟然還因為蟲子大喊大叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.71,0:13:03.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七月七日 在那之後已經4年了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.59,0:13:09.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.51,0:13:12.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是漂亮的枝條呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.56,0:13:15.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吧 多虧了我完美的指示呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.06,0:13:17.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是涼宮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.15,0:13:23.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我先說一下 這枝條可是用我的血換來的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看 這個勳章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 真的是很癢呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈？那不是全怪你們沒有注意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.16,0:13:37.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種失敗的證明還真的敢拿出來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難怪你會站在那麼遠的地方指揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道那裡蚊子很多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個傢伙！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.30,0:13:49.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要一直抓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.55,0:13:53.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我帶了止癢膏拿去用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.43,0:13:53.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幫大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.23,0:13:57.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你先用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.65,0:14:03.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 要怎麼裝飾屋子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.23,0:14:06.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也要考慮配色呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.24,0:14:10.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然連這裡也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,後背癢的地方 我可以幫你塗喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,背後也並沒有那麼癢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.17,0:14:22.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,並不需要塗藥 嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.38,0:14:24.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.34,0:14:32.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼涼宮 接下來幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.35,0:14:33.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.52,0:14:35.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是願望簽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.35,0:14:38.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,願望簽什麼的已經好久沒寫了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,寫點什麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.06,0:14:44.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想寫願望的話有個條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.19,0:14:46.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,條件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.49,0:14:46.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,提問
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.61,0:14:50.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在七夕能實現願望的是誰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牛郎星是天鷹座α星 織女星是天琴座α
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從距離來說 應該提前許十幾年的願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欸 猜中了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼子欺負人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.55,0:15:08.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.09,0:15:14.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就用 25或16年之前的條件來寫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.68,0:15:17.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是這只是單程吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.10,0:15:21.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,願望的路程應該是這個的兩倍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.02,0:15:24.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個問題 神會想辦法解決的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.27,0:15:27.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼宮應該會這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你到底想成為那傢伙的什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.24,0:15:34.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,願望 2個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 大家 寫好了就掛上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.29,0:15:43.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,春日 你寫了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.67,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\frz270\pos(626,443.6)}想和          一起玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.67,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(601.6,368.4)}U
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.67,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(601.6,408.4)}M
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.67,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(601.6,448.4)}A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.67,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\frz270\pos(1150.8,517.2)}外星人 未來人 超能力者 存在的話就來到我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這真是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.67,0:15:50.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你在想什麼失禮的東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你寫了什麼啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.10,0:15:58.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.39,0:16:03.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是庸俗加上只提升了點智能的高二的天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.02,0:16:06.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請把這叫成因果律的操作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要放哪好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.70,0:16:13.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.66,0:16:20.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇塞 你的願望棒極了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的也不差啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.04,0:16:26.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來你不僅僅是個變態啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.67,0:16:28.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋小市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.63,0:16:32.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 你不用掛那麼下面 我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔 交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.08,0:17:04.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿到外面來 看起來更有感覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.37,0:17:08.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 感覺願望真的都能實現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.17,0:17:11.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發生什麼事了吧 你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.85,0:17:21.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.84,0:17:28.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被另一個有希表白了什麼的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你 你怎麼知道的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊啦？我猜中啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.15,0:17:38.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有希的事 我剛聽涼子說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.32,0:17:42.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還看到你的態度 我就隨便問問而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.96,0:17:45.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.29,0:17:49.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後你就很在意了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,試著交往不就好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.25,0:17:53.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.88,0:17:57.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個長門跟現在的長門不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.76,0:18:00.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這事跟現在的長門沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:05.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是能這樣分清楚的話有多輕鬆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.73,0:18:07.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.15,0:18:12.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明對方都不記得了 自己還那麼在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.82,0:18:14.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,笨蛋嗎你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.86,0:18:20.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼宮跟阿虛也下來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不記得了啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.04,0:18:26.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,春日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.54,0:18:28.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走了 下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.05,0:18:41.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你在幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.22,0:18:48.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哈？這不是廢話嗎？非法人侵！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.90,0:18:54.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘛 來的正好 你也來幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.65,0:18:58.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒有阻止我 也就是說你也是共犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後呢 接著要幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.99,0:19:06.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幹嘛？這不很明顯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給外星人信息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.69,0:19:33.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.69,0:19:38.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我問你 你覺得外星人存在嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可能存在吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.23,0:20:12.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,記不起來也沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對自己來說很重要就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是為這而煩惱的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.36,0:20:21.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就盡量煩惱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.07,0:20:27.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是完全不覺得奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.33,0:20:29.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.54,0:20:35.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過為戀愛而煩惱的你倒是很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.21,0:20:40.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 到最後你只是想說這句話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.55,0:20:45.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然了 我的宗旨是萬物皆享受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.97,0:20:46.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下來的暑假 氣氛被破壞了就不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.06,0:20:54.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,確實如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.98,0:20:56.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉啊 春日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓你說這些不符你風格的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欠我一個大人情囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.72,0:21:26.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鶴屋學姐送來了糰子喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,春日喵好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們兩個也來一起吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好吃喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 吃東西的時候不要說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個時候的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在常識不斷增長之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.58,0:21:54.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不斷被忘卻的超常之物絕望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.87,0:21:56.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好熱鬧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是在那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.50,0:22:02.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然擺著一副不情願的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.88,0:22:05.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是幫我 認同我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.38,0:22:09.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個不是最後的一根嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.89,0:22:13.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.85,0:22:20.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我覺得我被救贖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.53,0:22:27.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.74,0:22:29.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,約翰史密斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.70,0:22:31.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是笨蛋嗎？
